# apps/worker + integrations

## Boundaries

- No LLM imports, no `apps/api` imports, no Postgres client
- No `CREDENTIAL_KEK`; fetch secrets via HMAC `POST /internal/credential-grants`
- BullMQ job payload: `taskId`, `userId`, `taskType`, `payload` only

## Workflows

- Task steps: `docs/specs/tasks/*.md` — deterministic, testable
- Playwright: per-user profile dir; apply `storageState` when grant provides it

## Logging

Never log passwords, `storageState`, or grant response bodies.

## Internal API client

Sign requests per `docs/specs/api-outline.md` (HMAC headers). Base URL from `API_INTERNAL_BASE_URL`.
